A tall cream-colored infographic poster uses a structured grid: a large typographic title at top, a seven-step process diagram across the upper middle, paired success/failure condition lists, equation panels, and a final recap strip at the bottom. The diagrams combine posets, cover graphs, path trajectories, contour maps, and emergent “good” symbols to show how local least-action rules scale into ordered structures or fail through hidden coupling. The palette is restrained but high-contrast, with black condensed type, deep red emphasis, teal headers, blue geometric accents, and a worn print texture.
